lead_paragraph: Arsenal closed in on another season of Champions League football with a 1-0 win over strugglers Norwich City in the Premier League on Saturday but it was another uncomfortable evening for manager Arsene Wenger amid protests from fans.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal Win Amid Anti-Wenger Protests, Newcastle Get Boost
